API Class

Source: R/classes.R
class_API.Rd

class_API object

Usage

class_API(
  type = "dcat:Dataset",
  accessLevel = "public",
  bureauCode = "009:38",
  programCode = "009:000",
  contactPoint = class_contactPoint(),
  dataQuality = TRUE,
  publisher = class_publisher(),
  references = character(0),
  title = character(0),
  description = character(0),
  accrualPeriodicity = character(0),
  issued = NULL,
  modified = NULL,
  released = NULL,
  temporal = character(0),
  identifier = class_Identifier(),
  accessURL = character(0),
  resourcesAPI = class_Resources(),
  downloadURL = character(0),
  describedBy = character(0),
  landingPage = character(0)
)

Arguments

type

<chr> type

accessLevel

<chr> Dataset access level

bureauCode

<chr> Dataset bureau code

programCode

<chr> Dataset program code

contactPoint

<S7_class>

dataQuality

<lgl> Dataset data quality

publisher

<S7_class>

references

<chr> Dataset references

title

<chr> Dataset title

description

<chr> Dataset description

accrualPeriodicity

<chr> Dataset update frequency

issued

<chr> Date Dataset was issued

modified

<chr> Date Dataset was last modified

released

<chr> Date Dataset was released

temporal

<chr> Date range the Current dataset covers

identifier

<S7_class> dcat:Dataset url and nrows in dataset

accessURL

<chr> dcat:Distribution url

resourcesAPI

<S7_class> data.frame of available supplemental resources

downloadURL

<chr> dcat:Distribution url to csv versions

describedBy

<chr> Hyperlink to Data dictionary

landingPage

<chr> Hyperlink to API landing page

Value

<S7_class> object
